---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="Kingdom Messenger Collective — Spirit Media"
	description="The Kingdom Messenger Collective — Spirit Media's flagship partnership program walking Kingdom Messengers through a 3+ year journey from restoration to proclamation."
>
	<main id="main-content">

		<!-- HERO -->
		<section class="bg-red-600 text-white py-24 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center">
				<p class="text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-200 mb-4">
					Flagship Partnership Program
				</p>
				<h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold leading-tight mb-6">
					The Kingdom Messenger Collective
				</h1>
				<blockquote class="text-red-100 italic text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed mb-8">
					"The Holy Spirit empowers you to be my messenger, telling people about me everywhere —
					to those close to you, those different from you, and to the remotest places on earth!"
					<cite class="block mt-2 text-red-200 text-sm not-italic font-semibold">— Acts 1:8 (FHB)</cite>
				</blockquote>
				<a
					href="mailto:kevin@spiritmedia.us"
					class="inline-block bg-white text-red-600 font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-50 transition-colors"
				>
					Apply for a Discovery Interview
				</a>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ARE YOU A KINGDOM MESSENGER -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
					Are You a Kingdom Messenger?
				</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
					You carry a message from God that has been refined through years of prayer, crushing,
					and surrender. You've seen enough fruit to know it has power to transform lives. But
					you don't just see a message — you see a movement.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-700 text-lg leading-relaxed font-medium">
					The question is: how do you move from message to movement?
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- FROM MESSAGE TO MOVEMENT -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">From Message to Movement</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					When Jesus said "Come, follow me," He wasn't inviting people to hear a talk — He was
					inviting them into a movement. The Kingdom Messenger Collective is our flagship
					partnership program, designed to walk with you through a <strong>3+ year journey from
					restoration to proclamation</strong>, and from message to sustainable global movement.
				</p>
				<div class="bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-600 p-6 rounded-r-xl">
					<p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold leading-relaxed">
						This isn't coaching. It's a covenant relationship. You bring the message. Spirit Media
						provides the platform, the strategy, and the team.
					</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- YOUR MENTOR: KEVIN WHITE -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">Your Mentor: Kevin White</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					Kevin White is an international bestselling author of seven books in five years. His
					first title, <em>Audacious Generosity</em>, was a bestseller in India before reaching
					the USA. His second book has over 2 million downloads in Nepal. Through weekly video
					podcasts over 7+ years, Kevin has reached audiences in 163 countries.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					As founder and CEO of Spirit Media, he has helped publish over 300 books for authors
					across the globe.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
					For over 40 years, God has used Kevin to raise up and commission Kingdom Messengers.
					Now, he invites you to walk the same path.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- MESSENGER SOUL CARE -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">
					Messenger Soul Care
				</h2>
				<p class="text-center text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-10">
					Every Kingdom Messenger receives personalized pastoral accompaniment:
				</p>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Weekly Private Calls</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							30-minute sessions with Kevin White. Father-focused development through prayer,
							discernment, and counsel for family, business, and ministry.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Monthly Mastermind</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							Iron sharpens iron. Gather with fellow Kingdom Messengers for encouragement,
							accountability, and shared wisdom.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Ongoing Access</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							Direct connection to Kevin for advice and encouragement between sessions.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6">
						<h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Quarterly Reviews</h3>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							Dedicated time to assess goals, celebrate progress, and chart next steps for
							your movement.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THE FORMATION PATHWAY -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-12 text-center">
					The Formation Pathway
				</h2>
				<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
					<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-2">Phase 1</p>
						<h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Heart</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium mb-3">
							Restoring the Father/Child Relationship
						</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							Intimacy with Father. Identity from Father. Inheritance through Father. We prioritize
							His work in you — becoming the healthiest adult version of yourself through inner
							healing, forgiveness, freedom, and transformational prayer ministry.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-2">Phase 2</p>
						<h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Message</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium mb-3">Entering the Kingdom</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							Discovering the Kingdom through Father's heart, through brokenness, and through
							community. Living God's Word with discipline, generosity, and celebration. Stepping
							into your role as king, priest, and minister.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border-t-4 border-red-600">
						<p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-600 mb-2">Phase 3</p>
						<h3 class="font-serif text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Movement</h3>
						<p class="text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium mb-3">Doing the Stuff</p>
						<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
							Restoration. Healing. Deliverance. Transformation. Taking everything the Father
							has built in you and releasing it through you — to the nations.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- THE 3-YEAR JOURNEY -->
		<section class="bg-gray-50 py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-10 text-center">
					The 3-Year Journey
				</h2>
				<div class="space-y-6">
					{
						[
							{
								year: 'Year 1 — Foundation',
								desc: 'Build your platform, publish your first or next book, establish your initial community.',
							},
							{
								year: 'Year 2 — Growth',
								desc: 'Multiple books, expanding audience, new revenue streams, deepening influence.',
							},
							{
								year: 'Year 3 — Movement',
								desc: 'Train leaders, expand globally, develop legacy systems.',
							},
							{
								year: 'Beyond — Multiplication',
								desc: 'Generational impact. Global Kingdom influence.',
							},
						].map(({ year, desc }) => (
							<div class="flex gap-4 items-start">
								<div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-600 mt-1.5 flex-shrink-0"></div>
								<div>
									<p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">{year}</p>
									<p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">{desc}</p>
								</div>
							</div>
						))
					}
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- MOVEMENT-BUILDING SERVICES -->
		<section class="bg-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">
					Movement-Building Services
				</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
					Spirit Media provides the full infrastructure for your movement — publishing, video
					production, digital presence, community platform, podcast, social media, and marketing.
					All done for you.
				</p>
				<p class="text-gray-900 font-semibold text-lg">
					You focus on your message. We build everything around it.
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

		<!-- ARE YOU ONE OF THE 10 -->
		<section class="bg-navy-950 text-white py-20 px-4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center">
				<h2 class="font-serif text-3xl font-bold mb-4">Are You One of the 10?</h2>
				<p class="text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-6">
					This opportunity is by invitation only, limited to <strong class="text-white">10 Kingdom
					Messengers per mastermind group.</strong> You may be a fit if you have:
				</p>
				<ul class="text-left space-y-3 max-w-md mx-auto mb-10">
					{
						[
							'A passion for God\'s presence and glory',
							'A clear calling to global Kingdom influence',
							'A message that demands a movement',
							'Commitment to a multi-year journey',
							'A heart for reaching the nations',
						].map((item) => (
							<li class="flex items-start gap-3 text-gray-300">
								<span class="text-red-400 mt-1">✓</span>
								{item}
							</li>
						))
					}
				</ul>
				<a
					href="mailto:kevin@spiritmedia.us"
					class="inline-block bg-red-600 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-md hover:bg-red-700 transition-colors"
				>
					Apply for a Discovery Interview
				</a>
				<p class="text-gray-500 text-sm mt-3">
					Email: kevin@spiritmedia.us
				</p>
			</div>
		</section>

	</main>
</Layout>
